{{flavour|A ring that provides protection from fire.}}

A [[ring of protection from fire]] protects its wearer from fire-based attacks, providing one level of [[fire resistance]] (rF+).

==Strategy==
As fire-based attacks are fairly frequent, a player will usually want at least a single level of fire resistance constantly. Thus, many players will choose to wear one of these rings constantly, although using it as a swap is usually a viable strategy as well.

